text: Somatocleptes apicicornis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fauvel in 1906, originally under the genus Microcleptes.BioLib.cz - Somatocleptes apicicornis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1906
title: Somatocleptes apicicornis
